r%2C%2023%2C%20is%20being%20held%20in%20Rikers%20Island%20awaiting%20the%20unsealing%20of%20his%20indictment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20prosecutors%20say%20he%20tricked%20100%20victims%20into%20turning%20over%20their%20crypto%20passwords.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20young%20Brooklyn%20man%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20stealing%20%2415%20million%20by%20impersonating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcoinbase%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECoinbase%3C%2Fa%3E%20customer%20care%20representative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20Ronald%20Spektor%2C%2023%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20tricking%20some%20100%20victims%20from%20across%20the%20United%20States%20into%20turning%20over%20the%20passwords%20for%20their%20cryptocurrency%20accounts%2C%20under%20the%20guise%20that%20their%20assets%20were%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Blong%20term%20larceny%20scheme%26quot%3B%20began%20in%20April%202023%20and%20continued%20until%20his%20arrest%20on%20December%204%2C%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%20Since%20then%2C%20Spektor%20has%20been%20held%20in%20Rikers%20Island%2C%20in%20lieu%20of%20bail%20set%20at%20%24500%2C000%20cash%20or%20%241%20million%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpektor%20faces%20top%20charges%20of%20grand%20larceny%20and%20money%20laundering%2C%20each%20carrying%20a%20maximum%20sentence%20of%2025%20years%20in%20prison.%20He%20is%20also%20charged%20with%20possessing%20stolen%20property%20and%20the%20personal%20information%20of%20his%20alleged%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Spektor%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20attorney%2C%20Todd%20Spodek%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20working%20to%20secure%20his%20release%20early%20next%20week%20and%20will%20challenge%20the%20charges%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2070%20victims%20have%20been%20interviewed%20by%20investigators%20with%20the%20NYPD%20and%20the%20Kings%20County%20District%20Attorney's%20Office%2C%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20Coinbase%20user%20confirmed%20that%20prior%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20cryptocurrency%2C%20said%20Coinbase%20users%20were%20contacted%20over%20the%20phone%20by%20someone%20who%20purported%20to%20be%20a%20legitimate%20Coinbase%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20allege%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20purported%20employee%20informed%20them%20their%20assets%20were%20at%20risk%20and%20needed%20to%20be%20moved%20to%20a%20new%20wallet%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20alleges%2C%20using%20the%20term%20for%20the%20applications%20that%20store%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelieving%20they%20were%20communicating%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20legitimate%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20victims%20then%20gave%20Spektor%20their%20seed%20phrases%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sequence%20of%2012%20to%2024%20words%20that%20act%20like%20a%20password%20%E2%80%94%20and%20moved%20their%20cryptocurrency%20to%20wallets%20that%20Spektor%20controlled%2C%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20cryptocurrency%20was%20immediately%20withdrawn%20without%20their%20permission%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20continues.%20The%20stolen%20crypto%20then%20%26quot%3Bpassed%20through%20cryptocurrency%20wallets%20belonging%20to%20the%20defendant%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20Coinbase%20user%20in%20California%20lost%20more%20than%20%246%20million%2C%20and%20another%20user%20from%20California%20lost%20%241%20million%2C%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestigators%20traced%20more%20than%20%245%20million%20in%20stolen%20funds%20to%20Spektor's%20accounts%20with%20two%20online%20gambling%20services%2C%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%20Millions%20more%20were%20converted%20into%20cash%20or%20laundered%20through%20online%20coin%20swapping%20services%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpektor's%20iPhone%20contained%20a%20wealth%20of%20incriminating%20evidence%2C%20investigators%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20alleges%20that%20this%20includes%20conversations%20on%20the%20online%20platform%20Discord%20in%20which%20he%20bragged%20%26quot%3Bthat%20he%20had%20made%20millions%20of%20dollars'%20worth%20of%20cryptocurrency%20through%20scamming%2C%20used%20social%20engineering%20to%20obtain%20Coinbase%20seed%20phrases%2C%20and%20had%20lost%20six%20million%20dollars%20worth%20of%20cryptocurrency%20through%20gambling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%20also%20contained%20communications%20with%20his%20father%20from%20November%202024%20in%20which%20%26quot%3Bthey%20discussed%2C%20in%20sum%20and%20substance%2C%20concealing%20the%20financial%20proceeds%20of%20the%20Coinbase%20scheme.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20continues%2C%20%26quot%3BOther%20messages%20show%20that%20the%20defendant%20asked%20his%20father%20to%20dispose%20of%20his%20hardware%20wallets%26quot%3B%20and%20asked%20his%20mother%20%26quot%3Bto%20purchase%20a%20new%20hardware%20wallet.%26quot%3B%20Hardware%20wallets%20are%20devices%20resembling%20USB%20drives%20that%20store%20private%20cryptocurrency%20data%20offline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpektor's%20Telegram%20handle%20was%20%26quot%3B%40LOLIMFEELINGEVIL%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20account%20included%20discussions%20%26quot%3Bof%20successful%20Coinbase%20phishing%20attacks%2C%20and%20efforts%20to%20recruit%20others%20to%20join%20the%20scheme%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20also%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20a%20Google%20account%20associated%20with%20Spektor%20contained%20%26quot%3Bapproximately%2029%20text%20messages%20containing%20personal%20identifying%20information%20in%20the%20form%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20individuals'%20email%20addresses%20and%20associated%20passwords.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpektor's%20attorney%2C%20Spodek%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20his%20client%20has%20been%20aware%20of%20th