ance%20to%20go%20to%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20outset%20of%20a%20Monday%20afternoon%20hearing%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Jed%20Rakoff%20unfavorably%20compared%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-victim-lawsuits-bank-of-america-bny-mellon-fast-track-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elawsuits%20against%20Bank%20of%20America%20and%20BNY%20Mellon%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20two%20similar%20lawsuits%20he%20had%20previously%20overseen%2C%20against%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20Deutsche%20Bank.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjp-morgan-settles-virgin-islands-jeffrey-epstein-sex-trafficking-suit-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EJPMorgan%20agreed%20to%20settle%20the%20case%20for%20%24290%20million%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-victims-5-million-deutsche-bank-settlement-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDeutsche%20Bank%20agreed%20to%20settle%20for%20%2475%20million%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERakoff%20said%20the%20language%20in%20the%20lawsuits%20against%20Bank%20of%20America%20and%20BNY%20Mellon%20%E2%80%94%20which%20were%20brought%20by%20the%20same%20attorneys%20and%20filed%20in%20October%20%E2%80%94%20was%20%26quot%3Bfrequently%20conclusory%26quot%3B%20and%20appeared%20to%20lack%20sufficient%20detail%20to%20demonstrate%20what%20the%20banks%20did%20wrong.%20He%20called%20the%20lawsuits%20%26quot%3Ba%20model%20of%20high-pitched%20rhetoric.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Knows'%20without%20saying%20by%20whom%20is%20vague.%20'Affiliated'%20without%20saying%20what%20that%20means%20is%20vague%2C%26quot%3B%20Rakoff%20told%20David%20Boies%2C%20an%20attorney%20who%20brought%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20that%20language%20is%20in%20the%20complaint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20hearin