s%26quot%3B%20to%20Epstein%20and%20his%20associates.%20Felicia%20Ellsworth%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20WilmerHale%2C%20said%20the%20plaintiffs%20couldn't%20prove%20anyone%20at%20BNY%20Mellon%20had%20the%20%26quot%3Bstate%20of%20mind%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20found%20liable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoies%20told%20Rakoff%20that%20the%20banks%20should%20have%20noticed%20enough%20smoke%20around%20the%20transactions%20from%20bank%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20Epstein%20and%20his%20associates%20to%20know%20there%20was%20a%20fire.%20Aside%20from%20Epstein's%202008%20criminal%20conviction%20in%20Florida%2C%20he%20had%20been%20dogged%20by%20civil%20litigation%20for%20years%2C%20Boies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERakoff%20expressed%20skepticism%20that%20the%20pattern%20of%20facts%20alleged%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20would%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLast%20I%20checked%2C%20that's%20not%20enough%20to%20survive%20a%20motion%20to%20dismiss%2C%26quot%3B%20Rakoff%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20have%20enough%20allegations%20as%20to%20specific%20facts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20hearing%2C%20lawyers%20for%20the%20Epstein%20victims%20appeared%20eager%20to%20revise%20their%20lawsuits%20and%20include%20the%20information%20they%20obtained%20through%20the%20discovery%20process.%20Rakoff%20said%20that%20material%20may%20be%20redacted%20on%20the%20public%20docket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he's%20giving%20us%20a%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20Sigrid%20McCawley%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20Boies%20Schiller%20Flexner%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-victim-lawsuits-bank-of-america-bny-mellon-judge-skeptical-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765837916000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6940802564858d02d216d6b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-victim-lawsuits-bank-of-america-bny-mellon-judge-skeptical-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20victims'%20lawsuits%20resembled%20two%20others%2C%20against%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20Deutsche%20Bank%2C%20which%20settled%20for%20hundreds%20of%20millions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-victim-lawsuits-bank-of-america-bny-mellon-judge-skeptical-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netflix's%20bid%20to%20buy%20Warner%20Bros.%20hinges%20on%20a%20key%20question%3A%20Who%20does%20it%20actually%20compete%20with%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Netflix%20Stranger%20Things%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69406cc6832e0ef1ead63fbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BStranger%20Things%26quot%3B%20maker%20Netflix%20could%20face%20regulatory%20scrutiny%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20buy%20Warner%20Bros.%3Cp%3ECOURTESY%20OF%20NETFLIX%2FCourtesy%20of%20Netflix%2FNetflix%20%C2%A9%202025%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENetflix%20has%20agreed%20to%20buy%20Warner%20Bros.%20in%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20deals%20in%20Hollywood's%20history.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGovernment%20regulators%20must%20decide%20whether%20Netflix%20would%20be%20too%20powerful%20with%20key%20WBD%20assets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20major%20question%3A%20Who%20does%20Netflix%20actually%20compete%20with%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWould%20buying%20Warner%20Bros.%20give%20Netflix%20too%20much%20power%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20streaming%20giant%20is%20telling%20regulators%20it%20won't%2C%20and%20antitrust%20experts%20say%20the%20answer%20ultimately%20depends%20on%20how%20you%20define%20who%20Netflix%20competes%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoes%20Netflix%20compete%20with%20only%20paid%20streaming%20services%2C%20a%20market%20where%20it%20dominates%3F%20What%20about%20the%20TV%20dinosaurs%20it%20disrupted%2C%20or%20the%20social%20video%20services%20nipping%20at%20its%20heels%3F%20Could%20sleep%20even%20be%20a%20competitor%2C%20as%20its%20cofounder%20Reed%20Hastings%20famously%20suggested%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-wbd-warner-bros-discovery-bidding-war-hollywood-comcast-netflix-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERival%20suitor%20Paramount%20Skydance%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20slammed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-warner-bros-discovery-deal-wont-repeat-past-acquisition-flops-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix-Warner%20Bros.%20mega-deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20anticompetitive%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20would%20harm%20consumers%20and%20Hollywood%20talent.%20Netflix%20is%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20paid%20subscription%20video%20streamer%2C%20and%20it%20would%20become%20even%20stronger%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20WBD's%20studio%20assets%2C%20including%20HBO%20and%20the%20Warner%20Bros.%20library%20(stocked%20with%20fare%20like%20Harry%20Potter%20and%20DC%20Comics).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20is%20advocating%20for%20a%20definition%20that%20considers%20total%20US%20TV%20viewing%20time.%20The%20streamer%2C%20which%20has%20expressed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-warner-bros-bid-trump-wbd-sarandos-peters-paramount-ellison-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfidence%20in%20its%20regulatory%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pointed%20to%20this%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20its%20employees%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20after%20combining%20with%20Warner%20Bros.%2C%20our%20view%20share%20would%20only%20move%20from%208%25%20to%209%25%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20still%20well%20behind%20YouTube%20(13%25)%20and%20a%20potential%20Paramount%2FWBD%20combination%20(14%25)%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-co-ceos-send-staffers-letter-about-warner-bros-deal-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix's%20co-CEOs%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20citing%20Nielsen%20data.%20A%20Netflix%20spokesperson%20referred%20to%20those%20remarks%20when%20asked%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConvincing%20antitrust%20regulators%20of%20that%20could%20be%20an%20uphill%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAntitrust%20regulators%20are%20likely%20to%20define%20the%20relevant%20market%20narrowly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anthony%20Palomba%2C%20a%20business%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia.%20%26quot%3BThe%20FTC%20and%20DOJ%20have%20consistently%20treated%20streaming%20as%20a%20discrete%20competitive%20arena%2C%20separate%20from%20linear%20television%2C%20theatrical%20distribution%2C%20or%20social%20video%20platforms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20Trump%20factor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20has%20said%20the%20Netflix-Warner%20Bros.%20deal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-netflix-warner-bros-acquisition-problem-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bcould%20be%20a%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20a%20very%20big%20market%20share%2C%20and%20when%20they%20have%20Warner%20Brothers%2C%20you%20know%2C%20that%20share%20goes%20up%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReuben%20Miller%2C%20the%20head%20of%20antitrust%20at%20financial%20data%20service%20Dealreporter%2C%20said%20Netflix's%20bid%20would%20%26quot%3Bbe%20challenged%20and%20litigated%20unless%20Netflix%20can%20convince%20Trump%20to%20come%20down%20on%20their%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20regulators%20could%20determine%20Netflix's%20competitive%20market%20and%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20future%20of%20the%20media%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb51abe6-0c49-48eb-9f2f-4940415b6373%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Netflix-Warner%20Bros.%20marriage%20would%20dominate%20paid%20streaming%20revenue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Netflix-Warner%20Bros.%20combination%20would%20be%20a%20colossus.%20Netflix%20and%20HBO%20Max%20have%20accounted%20for%2039%25%20of%20US%20paid%20subscription%20streaming%20revenue%20in%202025%2C%20per%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Market%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20firm%20with%2030%25%20to%2040%25%20market%20share%20has%20historically%20drawn%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20US%20government.%20If%20regulators%20see%20paid%20streamers%20as%20a%20distinct%20market%2C%20Netflix's%20Warner%20Bros.%20deal%20could%20be%20in%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SVOD%20rev%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69406a8464858d02d216d420%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENetflix%20and%20HBO%20Max%20make%20up%2039%25%20of%20paid%20streaming%20revenue%20in%20the%20US%20this%20year.%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Market%20Intelligence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20may%20not%20view%20social%20media%20apps%20%E2%80%94%20even%20when%20they%20are%20watched%20on%20a%20TV%20screen%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0as%20close%20substitutes%20for%20Netflix%2C%20Disney%2B%2C%20or%20Hulu%2C%20Palomba%20said.%20If%20so%2C%20a%20Netflix-HBO%20Max%20combination%20could%20limit%20choice%20or%20lead%20to%20price%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20few%20recent%20parallels%20to%20Netflix's%20Warner%20Bros.%20acquisition%2C%20Dealreporter's%20Miller%20said.%20One%20could%20be%20Charter%20Communications%2C%20which%20was%20allowed%20to%20expand%20its%20cable%20operation%20in%202016%2C%20though%20streamers%20were%20in%20their%20early%20days%20then.%20Miller%20said%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20government%20was%20protecting%20the%20nascent%20streaming%20industry.%20However%2C%20consumer%20behavior%20has%20changed%20so%20dramatically%20since%20then%20that%20he's%20unsure%20if%20those%20market%20definitions%20would%20be%20applicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incentive%20is%20to%20start%20with%20the%20assumption%20that%20a%20merger%20is%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20start%20with%20as%20narrow%20a%20definition%20as%20possible%2C%20so%20they'll%20probably%20start%20with%20paid%20streaming.%20And%20then%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20Netflix%20to%20try%20and%20get%20them%20to%20expand%20that%20market%20definition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298215b91-76ab-416e-8eef-9b79127d8471%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20paid%20and%20free%20streaming%20are%20competitors%2C%20Netflix's%20case%20looks%20better%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Netflix%20is%20easily%20the%20most%20viewed%20paid%20streamer%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20top%20streamer%20on%20TV%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20be%20free%20YouTube%2C%20whose%20viewership%20share%20has%20soared%20relative%20to%20Netflix%20in%20recent%20years.%20At%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20Netflix%20and%20YouTube%20each%20commanded%207.5%25%20of%20viewership%20on%20US%20TVs.%20But%20as%20of%20October%2C%20YouTube%20had%20a%2012.9%25%20share%20while%20Netflix%20took%20second%20place%20at%208%25%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nielsen.com%2Fdata-center%2Fthe-gauge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENielsen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20its%20paid%20peers%2C%20Netflix%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstreaming-inflation-price-increases-youtube-free-streamers-fast-netflix-disney-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattling%20free%20streamers%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20The%20Roku%20Channel%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftubi-nfl-game-free-stream-thanksgiving-gameplan-football-movie-documentary-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox's%20Tubi%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-fox-tubi-streamer-won-gen-z-grew-audience-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopular%20among%20Gen%20Z%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20adding%20free%20streamers%20into%20the%20marketplace%2C%20Netflix%20and%20HBO%20Max%20together%20accounted%20for%20just%20over%20a%20fifth%20of%20US%20streaming%20minutes%20in%20October%2C%20MoffettNathanson%20analyst%20Robert%20Fishman%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%20While%2020%25%20share%20is%20powerhouse%20status%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20a%20dealbreaker%20from%20an%20antitrust%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Streaming%20mins%20Oct%20MoffNath%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69406ab2832e0ef1ead63f83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENetflix's%20streaming%20minutes%20share%20in%20the%20US%20would%20be%20well%20behind%20YouTube%2C%20even%20with%20HBO%20Max.%3Cp%3EMoffettNathanson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b069ed44-ff9f-4774-bce9-b3793e19a7d0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20the%20total%20TV%20market%2C%20Netflix%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20combined%20would%20still%20be%20small%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20has%20argued%20that%20it's%20competing%20against%20all%20of%20traditional%20TV%2C%20not%20just%20streamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20viewership%20share%20ranks%20sixth%20among%20TV%20media%20distributors%2C%20versus%20its%20second-place%20spot%20in%20streaming.%20When%20measured%20against%20cable%20and%20broadcast%20TV%2C%20Netflix's%208%25%20share%20in%20October%20was%20slightly%20behind%20the%208.2%25%20share%20for%20Paramount%2C%20which%20includes%20its%20cable%20channels%20and%20CBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221532%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nielsen%20Oct%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69406afd04eda4732f2d8d3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22652%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENetflix%20is%20the%20sixth-largest%20TV%20media%20distributor%20by%20parent%20company%2C%20according%20to%20Nielsen.%3Cp%3ENielsen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20Netflix%20isn't%20trying%20to%20buy%20WBD's%20cable%20networks%20like%20CNN%2C%20it%20could%20argue%20that%20it's%20only%20adding%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20media%20conglomerate's%20viewership%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TV%20time%20Oct%20MoffNath%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69406a32832e0ef1ead63f71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENetflix%20could%20argue%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20Paramount%20and%20WBD%20would%20be%20even%20bigger%20than%20its%20own%20desired%20deal%20by%20one%20metric.%3Cp%3EMoffettNathanson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bea46e63-2c0a-40d1-b749-84e920431477%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndustry%20insiders%20and%20analysts%20doubt%20social%20media%20will%20count%20as%20competition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20would%20undoubtedly%20love%20a%20broad%20definition%20of%20its%20competitive%20market%20that%20includes%20TikTok%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20even%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-stream-bill-simmons-other-popular-video-podcasts-spotify-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20video%20games%2C%20which%20are%20also%20spaces%20where%20the%20streamer%20competes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20media%20insiders%20see%20an%20ultra-broad%20competitive%20landscape%20as%20a%20bridge%20too%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20clients%20are%20not%20pitching%20shows%20to%20YouTube%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20TV%20agent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorey%20Martin%20of%20LA-based%20law%20firm%20Granderson%20Des%20Rochers%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bto%20compare%20Netflix%20to%20YouTube%2C%20or%20even%20TikTok%2C%20is%20like%20comparing%20apples%20and%20oranges.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20same%20applied%20to%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumers%20tend%20to%20think%20of%20paid%20streamers%20like%20Netflix%20or%20Disney%2B%20when%20they%20want%20to%20watch%20movies%2C%20TV%2C%20or%20sports%2C%20Martin%20said%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthey%20don't%20necessarily%20think%20about%20YouTube%20or%20TikTok.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDirectly%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20say%20that%20a%20video%20game%20is%20competing%20with%20a%20movie%2C%20or%20a%20video%20game%20is%20competing%20with%20the%20TV%2C%20even%20though%20they%20do%20consume%20our%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul%20Telang%2C%20a%20business%20professor%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20see%20truth%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20an%20all-consuming%20battle%20for%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20analyst%20Laurent%20Yoon%20said%20Netflix%20may%20be%20a%20leader%20in%20long-form%20video%2C%20but%20others%20have%20better%20sports%20offerings.%20Yoon%20also%20wrote%20in%20a%20mid-December%20note%20that%20attention%20has%20shifted%20to%20short-form%20video%20on%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%2C%20and%20even%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-invests-micro-dramas-disney-fox-explore-the-format-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicro%20dramas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCritics%20may%20claim%20these%20are%20apples%20and%20oranges%2C%20but%20we%20heard%20the%20same%20argument%20about%20linear%20vs.%20streaming%20only%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Yoon%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-warner-bros-antitrust-analysis-paramount-skydance-regulators-social-media-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdi