ut%20it's%20clear%20that%20smart%20features%20are%20more%20of%20a%20bonus%20here.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20this%20is%20really%20a%20speaker%20that%20wants%20to%20play%20big%2C%20booming%20music.%20And%20to%20that%20end%2C%20it%20has%20impressed%20me%20nearly%20every%20time%20I%20listen%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be04bb2c-df1d-4064-878c-daee2581bdeb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20Echo%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20Echo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20Echo%20speakers%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20but%20Amazon's%20latest%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20strikes%20the%20perfect%20balance%20between%20smart%20features%20and%20audio%20quality.%20This%20larger%20take%20on%20the%20basic%20Echo%20Dot%20design%20features%20more%20robust%20drivers%2C%20with%20a%200.8-inch%20tweeter%20and%20a%202.5-inch%20woofer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20testing%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20the%20speaker's%20bass%20and%20audio%20range%2C%20especially%20for%20its%20size.%20It's%20larger%20than%20the%20Dot%20but%20still%20relatively%20compact%20and%20offers%20a%20deeper%20listening%20experience%20with%20plenty%20of%20volume%20to%20fill%20a%20living%20room.%20And%20as%20long%20as%20you%20don't%20push%20it%20too%20close%20to%20100%25%2C%20songs%20retain%20their%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Amazon%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20speaker%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6931fb9b71107c9f34576002%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20is%20Amazon's%20latest%20Alexa%20speaker%2C%20offering%20a%20notable%20upgrade%20in%20sound%20quality%20over%20the%20standard%20Echo%20Dot.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20the%20speaker's%20smarts%2C%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Echo%20devices%20built%20with%20Alexa%2B%20in%20mind%2C%20Amazon's%20new%20LLM%20(large%20language%20model)%20based%20voice%20assistant.%20With%20the%20improved%20Alexa%2C%20you%20can%20ask%20more%20complex%20questions%20or%20string%20multiple%20requests%20together%20in%20the%20same%20sentence.%20This%20type%20of%20digital%20assistant%2C%20which%20is%20much%20closer%20to%20ChatGPT%2C%20should%20open%20up%20a%20world%20of%20new%20uses%20as%20people%20try%20to%20interact%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20has%20a%20built-in%20smart%20home%20hub%20(Zigbee%2C%20Thread%2C%20Matter)%20to%20simplify%20pairing%20with%20other%20smart%20devices.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20the%20cheaper%20Echo%20Dot%20lacks.%20With%20the%20integrated%20hub%2C%20setting%20up%20control%20over%20your%20other%20devices%20requires%20fewer%20steps%2C%20and%20you%20get%20broader%20compatibility%20and%20more%20reliable%20connectivity.%20You%20also%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20getting%20a%20separate%20bridge%20for%20products%20that%20usually%20require%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20speaker's%20%24100%20retail%20price%2C%20the%20combination%20of%20its%20size%2C%20audio%20quality%2C%20and%20advanced%20smart%20home%20assistance%20makes%20it%20a%20great%20all-around%20smart%20speaker.%20Just%20be%20aware%20that%20Alexa%2B%20either%20requires%20an%20Amazon%20Prime%20membership%20or%20a%20separate%20%2420%20a%20month%20fee.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20Echo%20Dot%20Max%20will%20just%20use%20the%20standard%20version%20of%20Alexa%2C%20which%2C%20though%20still%20very%20useful%2C%20isn't%20as%20intelligent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b26e530f-4f1c-463b-8aa3-896919c13a13%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20Google%20Nest%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20Google%20Nest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nest%20Hub%20(2nd%20Gen)%20is%20the%20best%20smart%20speaker%20for%20any%20Google%20Home%20enthusiast.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20model%20is%20more%20than%20just%20a%20speaker%3B%20it's%20a%20smart%20display%20with%20a%20seven-in