2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Gemini%20is%20a%20big%20draw%2C%20I%20recommend%20waiting%20for%20the%20new%20model.%20But%20the%20Nest%20Hub%20(2nd%20Gen)%20remains%20an%20excellent%20option%20for%20those%20who%20want%20a%20Google%20smart%20display%20right%20now.%20I've%20been%20using%20the%20Nest%20Hub%20(2nd%20Gen)%20in%20my%20home%20since%20its%20release%2C%20and%20it%20continues%20to%20perform%20well.%20It%20might%20show%20some%20sluggishness%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20but%20mostly%20it's%20been%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20an%20even%20bigger%2C%2010-inch%20screen%2C%20there's%20also%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0c7cfe73be96e3be51c651854ff6f91ab6346e500e35b28fc396d83342cda772%26postID%3D6931ee6eaddd14a892c4235a%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-smart-speakers%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.officedepot.com%252Fa%252Fproducts%252F7601182%252FGoogle-Nest-Hub-Max-Smart-Home%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENext%20Hub%20Max%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20consider%2C%20which%20adds%20a%20camera%20and%20supports%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-nest-hub-2nd-gen-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Nest%20Hub%20(2nd%20Gen)%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2264281509-19af-445f-99d8-185ffa9ed58a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20with%20Siri%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20with%20Siri%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20around%20five%20years%20old%2C%20the%20Apple%20HomePod%20Mini%20remains%20a%20great%2C%20compact%20smart%20speaker.%20It's%20been%20refreshed%20with%20new%20colors%20over%20the%20years%2C%20so%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20styles%20that%20work%20well%20with%20different%20home%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HomePod%20Mini%20can%20get%20loud%20enough%20to%20be%20audible%20throughout%20a%20living%20room%2C%20but%20it's%20a%